{
  "text": "The curves of the distributions of subgraph centralities, mean subgraph centralities, and the relative deviations are plotted in Figures 6 and 7 , respectively. It was shown [CITATION_1] that scale-free characteristics of BA networks are independent of three parameters , 0 , and . So the algorithm of BA model was run with = 2500, 0 = 5, and = 3.",
